{"id": 2380, "genre": 1001, "title": "你如何看待学生表情动作全部被实时监控打分的“智慧课堂”？", "description": "今日全校课堂表情数据：中性2327、高兴1108、难过328、愤怒12、害怕0、反感440、惊讶 128。（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 3248, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201805290730363gZlcxQ2BFhmHnjb.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-29T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 284160, "content": "这样，是不是连上课都要学会表演……", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358463}, {"id": 284161, "content": "太讽刺了，物极必反", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841737}, {"id": 284162, "content": "1984里提到过的“脸罪”", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921494}, {"id": 284930, "content": "以前叫多一座学校少一座监狱。现在学校跟监狱看齐OTZ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923997}, {"id": 284163, "content": "就两个字 shabi。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355858}, {"id": 284165, "content": "黑镜 Arkangel 的前奏", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140376}, {"id": 284166, "content": "big brother is watching you", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333517}, {"id": 284167, "content": "人们越来越着急的想把未来变成便于统一管理的数据化模型。", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358480}, {"id": 284168, "content": "impressive", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322642}, {"id": 284169, "content": "那我玩手机玩的很开心是不是也的给他高分", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124537}, {"id": 284170, "content": "这有什么意义呢，真的能达到想象中的那种意义么", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347678}, {"id": 284171, "content": "傻", "image": "img/option/option/201805291425025PgOGuMIERCvk7sr.jpg", "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050590}, {"id": 284427, "content": "通过学生的微表情判断上课的时候的专注度和兴趣，虽然有点大动干戈了，但还是有用的\n就别瞎喷了，没考上清华北大的人多的是\n理智为上", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356229}, {"id": 284172, "content": "表情只会表现出他们的想法，并不能判断一个人是否聪明。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354425}, {"id": 284428, "content": "然后就有了个新名词:戏精式教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178030}, {"id": 285196, "content": "这要花多少钱啊，会不会很贵？", "image": "img/option/option/201806022303456JpQfXEtWFg4cdMC.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362080}, {"id": 284173, "content": "管天管地，管的着孩子们用什么样的表情上课？囚禁住孩子们的行动，怕是连心也一起绑住了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336043}, {"id": 285966, "content": "不明白为什么总是在这些莫名其妙得地方下功夫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367616}, {"id": 284175, "content": "感觉到了奴隶制的社会", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358503}, {"id": 284431, "content": "恶性循环", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359290}, {"id": 284176, "content": "课堂上的情绪识别与孩子平时成绩挂钩\n惊喜情绪高于10000 平时成绩90+\n惊喜情绪5000-10000 平时成绩80+\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1077644}, {"id": 296721, "content": "呵呵呵呵，这比监狱还差好吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1425655}, {"id": 284178, "content": "从小上学校服统一，怎么这一代连表情都要统一啦？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1177795}, {"id": 284179, "content": "Big brother is watching you.", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350932}, {"id": 284180, "content": "心理测量者", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 877242}, {"id": 285973, "content": "你能想象吗 我在上海某国际高中享受着同样待遇 上课被实时监控着", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366956}, {"id": 284182, "content": "我觉得没什么，还是该玩玩，该认真认真。这跟老师在讲台上一直看着你没啥区别。不要不这个作为评价学生的唯一标准就行", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193502}, {"id": 284438, "content": "欢迎来到panopticon ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124125}, {"id": 284183, "content": "和“三原色”一样恶心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354260}, {"id": 284184, "content": "big brother is watching you", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343300}, {"id": 284185, "content": "愤怒是怎么回事呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1206809}, {"id": 285209, "content": "学生可以有不听课的权利，但是要为自己的考试成绩负责。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362225}, {"id": 284187, "content": "幸亏毕业的早", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930392}, {"id": 284188, "content": "数字列宁主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358545}, {"id": 284189, "content": "带上面具，从学生做起吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358550}, {"id": 284451, "content": "不太合理！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355755}, {"id": 284196, "content": "没必要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332652}, {"id": 284452, "content": "处于试验阶段，实验结果可能还得几年才知道，又浪费了一批孩子啊！现在的教育，好多都在试验，试验，试验！没个几年怎么出结果？好多学生的品质，道德，学习天性，要么被遏制，要么被释放过火。而且试验过程一改再改！弄的面目全非！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355755}, {"id": 284197, "content": "有屁用！意义何在？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103806}, {"id": 284198, "content": "幸亏毕业的早", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1317843}, {"id": 284199, "content": "让孩子忘记了学习的初心，最后一部分会为表演而学习，为有人看到，大家赞赏而学习，更加大了内心的孤单", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1332652}, {"id": 284200, "content": "想起世界奇妙物语里的氛值教育", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357993}, {"id": 284201, "content": "疯人院？还是学校！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340432}, {"id": 284457, "content": "人工智能监控全人类的前奏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655046}, {"id": 286506, "content": "那么又会新增一门叫做表情管理的课程", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371265}, {"id": 284203, "content": "?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244783}, {"id": 286507, "content": "test", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371265}, {"id": 284204, "content": "累", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358585}, {"id": 284205, "content": "找不到看具体全文的地方。还是本来就是先给这么点信息？检测表情的话其实对研究学生心理活动，关注学生心理发展更有用吧。如果这个打分是为能更及时发现需要心理辅导的学生而存在的，而且打分以及判断结果都不会记录在档案影响升学就业，那我觉得OK啊。方法本无荒诞之说，只是看为了什么吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358584}, {"id": 284206, "content": "移民廣告", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350623}]}